0-x-12702.jpg" alt="德雷克和肯德里克·拉马尔。照片来源：305pics/GC Images；阿斯特丽达·瓦利戈尔斯基/WireImage" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/drake-kendrick-lamar-@-2000-x-12702.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/drake-kendrick-lamar-@-2000-x-12702-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/drake-kendrick-lamar-@-2000-x-12702-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/drake-kendrick-lamar-@-2000-x-12702-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/drake-kendrick-lamar-@-2000-x-12702-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/drake-kendrick-lamar-@-2000-x-12702-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3754887" class="wp-caption-text">德雷克和肯德里克·拉马尔。照片来源：305pics/GC Images；阿斯特丽达·瓦利戈尔斯基/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>早在四月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">拉马尔和德雷克就展开了一场严厉的说唱大战，</a>拉马尔在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">《Future》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metro-boomin">《Metro Boomin</a> 》中指责加拿大说唱歌手和科尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-takes-aim-at-drake-and-j-cole-on-metro-boomins-like-that-fuck-sneak-dissin-first-person-shooter-3608327">“Like That”</a> 。这位“No Role Modelz”明星最初确实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/j-cole-drops-surprise-album-might-delete-later-appears-to-hit-back-at-kendrick-lamar-diss-3613642">在混音带“稍后删除”中回复了“7 分钟练习”，</a>但随后撤回了 diss 曲目并迅速道歉。</p><p>德雷克与拉马尔之间的冲突在今年五月停止，这位多伦多球星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-claims-he-fed-kendrick-lamar-false-intel-on-new-diss-the-heart-part-6-3753644">放弃了《心之六》</a> ，他在节目中表示他的团队向拉马尔提供了虚假信息，并否认了在《拜见格雷厄姆一家》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-denies-paedophile-allegations-in-new-kendrick-lamar-diss-track-3753665">《不是》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-denies-paedophile-allegations-in-new-kendrick-lamar-diss-track-3753665">中针对他游说恋童癖的指控</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-denies-paedophile-allegations-in-new-kendrick-lamar-diss-track-3753665">像我们一样</a>&#39;。</p><p> 《Not Like Us》从此成为拉马尔最成功的歌曲之一，第四次登上公告牌排行榜第一名，并打破了 Spotify 嘻哈歌曲单日播放次数最多的记录。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-kendrick-lamar-performed-at-his-the-pop-out-ken-friends-concert-in-los-angeles-3767091">门票全部售完的六月节“Pop Out”音乐会上</a>，拉马尔六次演奏了这首歌——Dr <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dr-dre">. Dre</a>第一次介绍了这首歌，低声念出开场歌词： <i>“我看到死人。”</i></p><p>整个不和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-documentary-public-enemies-to-explore-kendrick-lamar-and-drake-feud-3800851">将在一部名为《公众之敌：肯德里克与德雷克》的新纪录片中进行探讨</a><em>。</em>据报道，该项目已获得 Channel 4 的批准，但尚未公布发布日期。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-drake-and-his-dad-crash-a-jazz-performance-in-toronto-and-sing-a-duet-3803472">《Watch Drake 和他的父亲在多伦多参加爵士乐演出并合唱二重唱》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
